e=\"presentation\"></li><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nua1719397360028.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nua1719397360028.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nua1719397360028.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qcg1665702560609\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__delete_213732\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Deletes the current occurrence from the database.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__topic_d70628e1_d70629e1_d70630e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__p_d70631e1_d70632e1_d70633e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">delete</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__topic_d46352e1_d46353e1_d46354e1_d46355e1_d46356e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d802147e65\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__2\">\n Data was successfully deleted.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__1\">\n -1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__2\">\n No entities are painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__1\">\n -2\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__2\">\n Occurrence not found.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__1\">\n -3\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__2\">\n Exceptional I/O error (hardware or software).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__1\">\n -5\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__2\">\n Update request for non-updatable occurrence.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__1\">\n -6\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__2\">\n Exceptional I/O error on write request; for example, lack of disk space, no write permission, or violation of a database constraint. Check the message frame for details.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__1\">\n -11\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__2\">\n Occurrence already locked.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__1\">\n -16\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6290e1_d6291e1_d6292e1__entry__2\">\n Network error: unknown.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">delete</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code>  through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-12</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UIOSERR_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Errors during database I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-30</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UNETERR_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Errors during network I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UGENERR_ERROR&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qcg1665702560609__table_d6293e1_d6294e1_d6295e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n An error occurred. No entities are painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__topic_d46357e1_d46358e1_d46359e1_d46360e1_d46361e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d802147e281\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__topic_d46362e1_d46363e1_d46364e1_d46365e1_d46366e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d802147e290\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__p_d70646e1_d70647e1_d70648e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">delete</span> statement deletes the current occurrence from the database.</p>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__note_w1681ab1b7b9b5_w1682ab1b7b9_w1683ab1b7_w1684ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> use this\n            statement only in the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">delete</span> trigger and, with extreme caution, in\n            the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">deleteUp</span> trigger. If you do place it in another trigger, make\n            sure that you lock the occurrence as soon as possible.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__section_u5z_fzb_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d802147e312\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">delete</span></h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qcg1665702560609__pre_sjm_31c_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger Delete\ndelete\nend ; Delete</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tao1720020794963.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>erase</a><p>Activate the delete or deleteUp trigger for all occurrences in the component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpg1665702560533.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>remocc</a><p>Mark an occurrence of the specified entity for deletion at the next store.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kgi1665702560769.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>store</a><p>Initiate validation and storage of all occurrences marked as modified. It activates the appropriate validation triggers as required, followed by the write and delete triggers.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mfn1665703129379.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger delete</a><p>Removes occurrences marked for deletion, when writing updates to the database.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dkk1665702703541.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger deleteUp</a><p>System trigger that handles deletion of Up entity occurrences. (An Up entity is an inner entity that represents the One side in a one-to-many relationship.)</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvb1665703130778.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger store</a><p>Trigger that responds to a request to save (store) the data.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422566\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422566\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "delete Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Version: Use up/down arrow keys to navigate, Esc to collapse. Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0 Reflection Desktop User Guide (German) Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German) Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1 Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0 Reflection Desktop User Guide (German) Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German) Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1 Last Updated Juli 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Deletes the current occurrence from the database. delete Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $status Value Meaning 0 Data was successfully deleted. -1 No entities are painted on the component. -2 Occurrence not found. -3 Exceptional I/O error (hardware or software). -5 Update request for non-updatable occurrence. -6 Exceptional I/O error on write request; for example, lack of disk space, no write permission, or violation of a database constraint. Check the message frame for details. -11 Occurrence already locked. -16 Network error: unknown. Table 2. Values commonly returned by $procerror following delete Value Error constant Meaning -2 through -12 <UIOSERR_*> Errors during database I/O. -16 through -30 <UNETERR_*> Errors during network I/O. -1 <UGENERR_ERROR> An error occurred. No entities are painted on the component. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The delete statement deletes the current occurrence from the database. CAUTION: use this statement only in the delete trigger and, with extreme caution, in the deleteUp trigger. If you do place it in another trigger, make sure that you lock the occurrence as soon as possible. Example: Using delete trigger Delete delete end ; Delete Copy Related Links erase Activate the delete or deleteUp trigger for all occurrences in the component. remocc Mark an occurrence of the specified entity for deletion at the next store. store Initiate validation and storage of all occurrences marked as modified. It activates the appropriate validation triggers as required, followed by the write and delete triggers. trigger delete Removes occurrences marked for deletion, when writing updates to the database. trigger deleteUp System trigger that handles deletion of Up entity occurrences. (An Up entity is an inner entity that represents the One side in a one-to-many relationship.) trigger store Trigger that responds to a request to save (store) the data. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}